      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "DRAMATICAL (3) shapes well for this after a dazzling last start success, getting around The Meadows over 525m in 29.57. In form and rates on top again. DEWANA STAR (1) is yet to be beaten here, scoring four wins from as many starts. In the money last time at Healesville (16.39) in a Special conditions race, finishing a neck second. Can hit the frame with the right run. BLESSED RAIN (4) won comfortably last time scoring by 9 lengths at this track after jumping from box 4 (21.59). Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. One of the prime contenders. TRIBECA (8) missed the frame latest (25.61) when eighth over 450m at Ballarat in a Special conditions G2. Boasts a top strike-rate from this draw, winning three of five runs.",
